        "cmip6.atmoschem.stratospheric_heterogeneous_chemistry.overview": {
            "values": [
                "In the high top version of CESM2 (WACCM), the model contains all processes relevant to stratospheric chemistry, with a special emphasis on the capability to explicitly simulate ozone depletion. It also simulates the evolution of stratospheric aerosols, incuding volcanic eruptions.  This follows Mills et al. (2016, https://doi.org/10.1002/2015JD024290 ). "
